title: Dinner and a Movie (New Episode)
overview: Married for over 15 years, Biggs and Mollen will bring their shared love of film and food to TBS fans every Saturday night with a can't-miss party that includes fun games, delicious food and some of the biggest film blockbusters.Â Featuring a schedule of surprise guests, including a collection of familiar Food Network faces who will bring their cooking expertise and some delicious bites to share, "Dinner and a Movie" is a perfect blend of behind-the-scenes scoop and a potluck with friends.
